  "text": "We show results on 4 datasets: heart disease, breast cancer, diabetes and STAGGER [CITATION_1] . The first three are UCI datasets where we produce concepts using the technique described previously, while STAGGER is a popular artificial concept change problem. We vary the number of overlapping features to investigate how the severity of change affects performance.",
